							<handNote script="Hebrew" scope="sole"/>
						</handDesc>
						<additions>
							<p>Folios 316v and 317r contain a short treatise written in an Italian cursive script.</p>
							<p>Two Latin inscriptions, folios 1v and [320r].</p>
